Text: "It's all about traveling to kolkata alone.. For a week days\n      My journey\
  \ started with a WhatsApp status \"STARTED\" and my train came to warangal faltform..\
  \ And the journey is 2days in train then my mind started thinking how this 2days\
  \ will completed.. Then after compartment is filled up and I took a tour full compartment\
  \ and check down similar age of me but to my fate NO ONE is there took my seat watching\
  \ the green paddy fields moved on then after and 6hours journey some looks and smiles\
  \ exchange with Co passengers and its - T- time *Chaiwala came and real journey\
  \ came to start like a travel all my Co passenger are bengalis and I'm from telangana\
  \ they give me there best time to me chit charted for a while of 3hours and they\
  \ maid me stronge and happy they gave me full details about my doubts about kolkata\
  \ they best places to visit kolkata in a day best food to stay I remember how \"\
  I started but at the end made me happy and confident\".\n       From that journey\
  \ onwards I'm travelling solo and group\""
